 to Hate zone in Aggro (Not the hate revamp</span><hr size=1> With regard to noticing differences, I'm well aware that the Zone in isnt a safe spot, I've probably been to Hate on 30 seperate occaissions.  <br>
<br>
Its just that it has been consistant aggro _immediately_ on zone in as soon as a single person loses or zones in without invis up.  This happened several nights running.<br>
<br>
Further, assuming you kill the first wave of mobs with no problem, if you have to rez anyone or a shammy canabalizes down too low, it seems that low health aggro seems to consistantly pull another whole batch of mobs to there.<br>
<br>
The West Wall 'safe spot' camp appears to be completely unaffected, and we cleared the majority of floor 1 pulling to there each time.  Only the zone in seems this wacky.<br>
<br>
