<br>
We send our group of 60+ in with the CoH mage, they walk to the safe spot, and the rezzer camps; then we start the chain; they can get to the safe spot NP due to the tiny aggro range for a lvl 60+.  Then we port in for the CoH, first those 55-60, then those 50-55, then those 47-49 and that last group almost always gets aggro at the port in and someone dies, even if they go in invis. <p>Obon Took<br>
